_sText:
Here's my new awp map. I hope you like it. :D

Some extra stuff:
-many secrets and hints in the map
-much bases
-Deaglez, AWP's and hidden grenades
-destructable things
-clouds and other effects
-sniper bases (how to arrive: go into the hidden teleporter)
-death cliff



The installation is easier as easy:
Just extract the awp_stranded_final.bsp file into 
C:/Program Files/steam/steamapps/YourSteamName/Counter-Strike: Source/cstrike/maps


Have Phun! ;D




Made by Z3R0N1C.
